sentences: Before her debut, she served as a keyboard session for stages and album of Lucid Fall.
As a radio DJ, she hosted "아름다운 동요세상 (Beautiful World of Children's Songs)" on the education channel EBS from March 6, 2011 to February 28, 2012.

In 2007 she provided the singing voice of Giselle in the Korean dubbing of Enchanted, and in 2010 she provided the singing voice of Rapunzel in the Korean dubbing of Tangled in all the songs, except for Healing Incantation.
In 2014 she sang for the Korean dubbing of Tinker Bell and the Legend of the NeverBeast.
